OL,3,CWar veterans visit Jersey to learn
OL,4,Cmore about US links to Liberation
OL,6,FThe Jersey War Tunnels are a defiant
OL,7,Freminder of the island's occupation
OL,8,Fwhen German forces took control of the
OL,9,FChannel Islands during the Second
OL,10,FWorld War.
OL,12,FSeven US veterans followed in the
OL,13,Ffootsteps of those involved in
OL,14,Fsecuring the Channel Islands' liberty.
OL,16,FThe dwindling numbers of World War Two
OL,17,Fveterans make this visit even more
OL,18,Fpoignant.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
