OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781552859
OL,3,CWar veterans visit Jersey to learn
OL,4,Cmore about US links to Liberation
OL,6,FTheir duty was honoured by servicemen
OL,7,Ffrom the Vietnam, Iraq and Afghanistan
OL,8,Fwars.
OL,10,FJim Graham, a Vietnam War veteran, was
OL,11,Fjoined on this trip by his son, Todd
OL,12,FGraham, an Afghanistan veteran.
OL,14,FBoth spoke about a shared heritage
OL,15,Famong generations who served in the US
OL,16,Fmilitary, including American soldiers
OL,17,Fwho helped liberate the Channel
OL,18,FIslands.
OL,20,FTodd explained: "I think it's
OL,21,Fincredibly humbling.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781552859
OL,3,CWar veterans visit Jersey to learn
OL,4,Cmore about US links to Liberation
OL,6,F"Fighting for a country that many of
OL,7,Fthem probably didn't know any history
OL,8,Fabout and yet they felt a strong sense
OL,9,Fof purpose and mission, to be here to
OL,10,Fhelp the people of Jersey. US forces
OL,11,Fcoming through, it's pretty
OL,12,Fremarkable."
OL,14,FThe United States joined the war in
OL,15,F1941 following the surprise Japanese
OL,16,Fattack on Pearl Harbour.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
