PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781552859
OL,3,CWar veterans visit Jersey to learn
OL,4,Cmore about US links to Liberation
OL,6,FAmerica's involvement in the war was
OL,7,Fevident in the liberation of the
OL,8,FChannel Islands through Allied air and
OL,9,Fsea rescue operations and naval
OL,10,Fpatrols.
OL,12,FThis relatively unknown history drew
OL,13,Fthis group of American veterans to
OL,14,FJersey, with a desire and passion to
OL,15,Fkeep the stories and experiences of
OL,16,Ftheir World War Two comrades alive for
OL,17,Fgenerations to come.
OL,19,FThey also visited Noirmont Point to
OL,20,Fview the coastal artillery sites and
OL,21,Fthe Military Museum.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
