PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781552859
OL,3,CWar veterans visit Jersey to learn
OL,4,Cmore about US links to Liberation
OL,6,FThe veterans visiting the island were
OL,7,Fpart of a wider trip that included
OL,8,Fvisiting the Omaha beaches in Normandy
OL,9,Fahead of the D-Day anniversary on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FIt was clear when speaking with the
OL,13,Fgroup that retracing the past has
OL,14,Fprovided a source of hope for the
OL,15,Ffuture.
OL,17,FRetired Air Force veteran, Rob Ramos,
OL,18,Fsays we should look to the past as we
OL,19,Fhead into the future.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
