OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781552859
OL,3,CWar veterans visit Jersey to learn
OL,4,Cmore about US links to Liberation
OL,6,FHe said: "My hope as a military
OL,7,Fveteran is that we can remember these
OL,8,Flessons and not have to repeat them as
OL,9,Fhistory goes forward."
OL,11,FAs Jersey returns from the polls, ITV
OL,12,FChannel breaks down the key election
OL,13,Fresults. Listen to Jersey Votes
OL,14,Fwherever you get your podcasts or
OL,15,Fwatch on ITVX, and YouTube below, with
OL,16,Fnew episodes each Thursday...
